  "prompt": "What celebrities have converted to Islam?",
  "response": "Several celebrities have converted to Islam over the years. Here are a few notable ones:\n\n1. **Muhammad Ali** - The legendary boxer converted to Islam in 1964 and was known for his strong faith and advocacy for civil rights.\n\n2. **Kareem Abdul-Jabbar** - Former NBA star and Hall of Famer converted to Islam in 1971, changing his name from Lew Alcindor.\n\n3. **Cat Stevens (Yusuf Islam)** - The British musician converted to Islam in 1977 and changed his name to Yusuf Islam. He left the music industry for a time but later returned to it.\n\n4. **Mike Tyson** - The former heavyweight boxing champion converted to Islam during his time in prison in the 1990s.\n\n5. **Sinead O'Connor** - The Irish singer announced her conversion to Islam in 2018 and changed her name to Shuhada\u2019 Sadaqat.\n\n6. **Ellen Burstyn** - The Academy Award-winning actress practiced Sufism, a mystical Islamic belief, and converted in the 1970s.\n\n7. **Ice Cube** - The rapper and actor converted to Islam in the 1990s.\n\nThese are just a few examples, and there are many more individuals from various fields who have embraced Islam.",
